            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2">Abeo! seeks to fill this gap by creating an online platform to explore West African
                        food culture, with content relevant both to complete newcomers to West African cooking and those
                        who have been cooking and eating it their entire lives.
                        Users can dive into all aspects of culinary culture: ingredients, recipes and principles of
                        cooking. All elements of the website focus on creating a culture of accessibility. Users, for
                        example, can discover in-depth information about commonly used ingredients, track down local
                        suppliers or learn about substitutions.


                    </td>
