                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="2">I’m forever frustrated by the state of so many recipe pages online: they’re
                            often full of unnecessary and unwarranted information (“my husband normally hates peas, but
                            loves them in this recipe!!”) and take huge amounts of scrolling just to get to the elements
                            you want — the ingredients and the method. My pages are cleaner, more focused and easy to
                            navigate.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
