                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="2">Each of the recipe pages on Abeo! start with a short, informative introduction,
                            with further thoughts and notes hidden under a ‘read more’. If an ingredient or technique
                            could use more explanation, it is highlighted — the user can click on it to bring in
                            annotations with further explanation. The recipes themselves are very visual, offering a
                            helping hand to those who may find the ingredients unfamiliar.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
